{
  "stem": "22511.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's how I've taught my children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that's how I will die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I love people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "For me, no difference.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Just to be a mensch, a person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I become Shomer Hatzair, and I worked very nice in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We built kibbutzim-- you know what is kibbutz?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we'd send them to Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were-- because we was not allowed to travel to Israel, because we need quotas.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had-- we were sending with boats, like",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was very tough traveling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went with-- mine ship was I was travel-- first my sister-- sorry, I had to interrupt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister got sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had earache, very bad ears problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had to be operated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she had to be sent with first Aliyah to Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she went in 1945, and I had to go-- the first ship what was available, I had to be on it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to go with Aliyah Aleph, because I was very patriotic already.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am-- with all my heart, if I do something, I like to do it the right way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, I'd like to go with Aliyah Bet and I want to work for Israel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they sent me with Aliyah Bet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only before this, I was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We built kibbutzim in Krakow, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We done brushes, we had a little factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did produce brushes, and we had to sell them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not so easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the money went to a big-- to the-- for-- towards Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The money-- all money is supposed to go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we were sent to Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In Germany, we-- I was in-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Jordanbad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a kibbutz looked after also nuns, German nuns.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
